<template>

</template>

<script>
import axios from "axios";
    export default {
        props:['slug'],
        data(){
        return{
            jobInfo:[],
        }
        },
        mounted(){
            this.getInfo(this.rootDomain);
        },
        methods:{
          getInfo(){
            axios.get(this.rootDomain+'vue/v3/job/'+this.slug)
            .then((response)=>{
                console.log(response.data);
            })
            .catch((error)=>{
                console.log(error);
            });
          }
        }
}
</script>
